title: Ebro In The Morning - Ebro Reacts To The YSL RICO Charges + Callers With Weird Pets
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 5/12/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about the RICO charges brought towards YSL members, NBA Playoffs, the Yankees, and much more!

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
